item.description: Walking to the riva after getting gelato at Marco. Maybe these musicians were part of the ensemble playing on the temporary stage on Piazza Unita related to the Pope’s visit to Trieste. Enjoying the sun and the ocean breeze during a break. View this post on Instagram
